text: Amirhossein Yahyazadeh (, born 17 February 1998) is an Iranian footballer who plays as a winger who currently plays for Iranian club Pars Jonoubi Jam in the Persian Gulf Pro League. ==Club career== ===Naft Tehran=== He made his debut for Naft Tehran in 21 fixtures of the 2017–18 Iran Pro League against Gostaresh Foulad. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian footballers Category:Naft Tehran F.C. players Category:Pars Jonoubi Jam players Category:Khooneh be Khooneh players Category:People from Babolsar Category:Association football midfielders
